#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.31"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.31:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.31:0.2"
msgid "3. Bhāravagga "
msgstr "3. The Burden "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.31:0.3"
msgid "31. Aghamūlasutta "
msgstr "31. The Root of Misery "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn22.31:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.31:1.2"
msgid "“Aghañca, bhikkhave, desessāmi aghamūlañca. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you misery and the root of misery. "

msgctxt "sn22.31:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha. "
msgstr "Listen … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.31:1.4"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, aghaṃ? "
msgstr "And what is misery? "

msgctxt "sn22.31:1.5"
msgid "Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, aghaṃ, vedanā aghaṃ, saññā aghaṃ, saṅkhārā aghaṃ, viññāṇaṃ aghaṃ. "
msgstr "Form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness are misery. "

msgctxt "sn22.31:1.6"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, aghaṃ. "
msgstr "This is called misery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.31:1.7"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, aghamūlaṃ? "
msgstr "And what is the root of misery? "

#. VAR: nandīrāgasahagatā → nandirāgasahagatā (sabbattha)
msgctxt "sn22.31:1.8"
msgid "Yāyaṃ taṇhā ponobhavikā nandīrāgasahagatā tatratatrābhinandinī; "
msgstr "It’s the craving that leads to future lives, mixed up with relishing and greed, taking pleasure in various different realms. That is, "

msgctxt "sn22.31:1.9"
msgid "Seyyathidaṃ—kāmataṇhā, bhavataṇhā, vibhavataṇhā. "
msgstr "craving for sensual pleasures, craving to continue existence, and craving to end existence. "

msgctxt "sn22.31:1.10"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, aghamūlan”ti. "
msgstr "This is called the root of misery.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.31:1.11"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
